                                <li>The BiblioVélo guarantee provides for a compensatory payment to the Owner in the event that the Bike is reported missing, stolen or damaged, provided that the Owner and Borrower have both acted in accordance with this rental agreement and any other information we may provide about the BiblioVélo guarantee from time to time. </li>
