                                <li>It is the Owner’s responsibility to arrange pickup/dropoff of the Bike and to carry out the various checks we require under this rental agreement. We do not get involved in communications between Owners and Borrowers in respect of any booking. All communications between Owners and Borrowers must take place via our secure messaging system. </li>
                                <li>The Owner agrees that he/she shall not, other than in exercise of his/her rights under this agreement or applicable law, interfere with the Borrower’s possession of the Bike during the Hire Period.</li>
                                <li>
